name: Dickbutt
description: Launched on 10/12/2024 on the Base Chain, Dickbutt Token is a community-driven project inspired by one of the most iconic internet memes, “Dickbutt.” The project aims to blend humor and blockchain technology to create a lighthearted and engaging experience for its community. As a meme token, its purpose lies in fostering user engagement, building a strong online community, and exploring the intersection of internet culture and decentralized finance.
